		<word definition="The ability of an organism to keep its body temperature within certain boundaries.">thermoregulation</word>
		<word definition="The maintenance of constant osmotic pressure through variations in water/salt concentration.">osmoregulation</word>
		<word definition="Containing nitrogen.">nitrogenous</word>
		<word definition="Water soluable and nitrogenous product produced as a result of protein metabolism (mammals).">urea</word>
		<word definition="Filtration under high hydrostatic pressure which retains large molecules.">ultrafiltration</word>
