		<word definition="A gland which is located at the base of the brain and is the 'master gland' of the endocrine system.">pituitary gland</word>
		<word definition="Water created by a living organism through metabolism.">metabolic water</word>
		<word definition="The sac which surrounds the glomerulus at the start of the nephron. It is where ultrafiltration occurs.">Bowman's capsule</word>
		<word definition="A thin membrane of fibrous protein that sperates an epithelium from unerlying tissue.">basement membrane</word>
